=== Fan control ===

Fan control needs to be explicitly allowed:

{{File|/etc/modprobe.d/thinkpad_acpi.conf||<pre>
options thinkpad_acpi fan_control=1
</pre>}}

Turn off:

{{RootCmd|echo level 0 > /proc/acpi/ibm/fan}}

Maximum speed:

{{RootCmd|echo level 7 > /proc/acpi/ibm/fan}}

